cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NA 

This paper deals with image set classification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed algorithm involves metric learning, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The use of Riemannian manifolds and kernels suggests a focus on geometric deep learning and manifold learning (cs.AI, cs.MM). Finally, the application of the algorithm to face recognition and object categorization suggests a focus on computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.NA).
